{"tid":175671,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"荷蘭國家隊考慮重簽雲高爾","createTime":"2017-03-27T15:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-28T18:08:24.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c89d5708e465c073b8251020e897b141452911a9","tid":175671,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:53:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.performgroup.com/di/library/GOAL/f4/b8/louis-van-gaal_1clkzhcrnakgu1r9at61zw00pa.jpg?t=-1453947013&amp;w=620&amp;h=430\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.performgroup.com%2Fdi%2Flibrary%2FGOAL%2Ff4%2Fb8%2Flouis-van-gaal_1clkzhcrnakgu1r9at61zw00pa.jpg%3Ft%3D-1453947013%26w%3D620%26h%3D430&h=7c075a84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n荷蘭國家隊炒掉白蘭特之後，有傳他們想找雲高爾回歸教橙軍。<br />\n<br />\n雲高爾曾經帶領荷蘭在14世界盃拿到第3名，現在荷蘭有難，荷蘭足總有意請雲高爾回歸。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭足總在研究各種方案，包括以顧問形式讓雲高爾指點球隊。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭足總總監Jean Paul Decossaux表示，他們正在尋找技術總監，同時在尋找教練，並且提到雲高爾的名字。<br />\n<br />\n荷蘭足總總監Jean Paul Decossaux說：「我們正在尋找新教練，但不可能一個星期內成事，最快6月吧。名單中有不少名字，外國教練也可以。朗奴高文當然有力勝任，不過他和球會有合約。無論如何，荷蘭足球將要向前走。」<br />\n<br />\n敢帥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3afe8722aa32299ef05df0fcae08f636ce573eb","tid":175671,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T15:59:30.000Z","msg":"佢帶荷蘭係帶得幾好"},{"pid":"94fcc3544b46c8b7a226bdcc8bbc466f2eeb2cee","tid":175671,"uid":372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢帶荷蘭係帶得幾好</blockquote><br />\n帶曼嗰陣都ok"},{"pid":"d3aeb377a90dd2bd5a9fa3f467b56662b236f0ba","tid":175671,"uid":6136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>佢帶荷蘭係帶得幾好</blockquote><br />\n帶曼嗰陣都ok</blockquote><br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{