都係敢帥放權俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7876692f07d7180f35a3f1366fa206d0868ae61","tid":175671,"uid":74632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:31:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇新仔有眼光的 教波就冇人明佢喇</blockquote><br />\nmartial rashford<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nV92由阿積士到巴塞拜仁再到曼聯都捧起一炸新人<br />\n阿積士睇95歐聯陣容, 巴塞有VV沙維佩老大, 拜仁湯馬士梅拿同放小豬打中場中, 曼聯就馬迪爾,拉舒仲有科素文沙同波夫域積遜</blockquote><br />\n不過佢套戰術真係好悶</blockquote><br />\nV92第一水嘅巴塞係好轟烈嘅進攻足球來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實個時都好好睇呀<br />\n<br />\n前便:<br />\n李華度 古華特 Figo<br />\n<br />\n中場:<br />\n高古 哥帥 安歷基<br />\n<br />\n仲有一大班後備, 都係勁野, 個時係好好睇呀的波"},{"pid":"a752042d068b8e41406b149594a7a192d19fc590","tid":175671,"uid":31542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-28T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我記得8強個陣好似準備要輸球十二碼<br />\n雲膠爾即刻換門將 最後撲到十二碼 唔洗輸<br />\n唔記得有無記錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係啊 對哥斯達黎加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但4強唔知做乜9，冇換龍輸撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n換龍又真係俾佢救到2球<br />\n真係唔知講咩好</blockquote><br />\n係球球捉到路</blockquote><br />\n對阿根廷換左2個之後，雲佩斯已經冇氣踢少個，焗住換，同埋冇把握12碼必勝，對哥達都12碼，如果阿根廷把握力正常少少都贏2:0，唔會加時</blockquote><br />\n八強個陣時好佩服雲膠爾 加時107分鐘個陣夠膽換門將 之後盡猜到等互射十二碼<br />\n但對亞軍廷佢用哂換人名額<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n由個陣時開始更加佩服雲膠爾 但去到最聯個陣唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe31e29b5501be9beae495b850924fe68279c17b","tid":175671,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"